{"tid":597661,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"[live]零計劃、去函館","createTime":"2018-03-18T23:56:22.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-26T06:43:37.000Z","uid":8203,"like":11,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"93950516b347da551d1abce68297524e760dc9e7","tid":597661,"uid":8203,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-18T23:56:22.000Z","msg":"話說買左心動香草上北海道<br />\n函館時間靚d就唔去札幌了 雖然想去札幌多d<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/19/075252_6f9fcf4abf2f16b03bc820e628e662ec.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F03%2F19%2F075252_6f9fcf4abf2f16b03bc820e628e662ec.png&h=ca8cfceb&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/19/075255_c3a7f5867f6ee0e5ece5dedc1975a6fa.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F03%2F19%2F075255_c3a7f5867f6ee0e5ece5dedc1975a6fa.png&h=6d061d26&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n跑去車站都趕唔切原先計劃個班車<br />\nbook左十點正900円巴士過成田但而家呢班JR10:05先到<br />\n一陣唔知我張巴士飛仲有無效<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n第一次去北海道<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n有無巴打同一班機<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ce6c5946bb6eae40bce851a87ff669723f284e88","tid":597661,"uid":8203,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-19T00:02:54.000Z","msg":"到某個站有個隻手打石膏既肥佬<br />\n另外一個矮既阿婆上車<br />\n<br />\n優先席一個人都無<br />\n佢地都要格硬同其他人逼普通座位<br />\n唔知為乜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"61b77e04be6bb2f450b30d8b5205cc9107c02030","tid":597661,"uid":8203,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-19T00:21:38.000Z","msg":"成個車廂廂靜嚶嚶既時候總有一群後生女會好嘈<br />\n相信有去開日本既各位都經歷過<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d265fcb694c10d0307bfdb325a7f43ddf8c25ad1","tid":597661,"uid":8203,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-19T01:29:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/19/092656_45b7ad6b6c425ca6d7c951bc05e5d29e.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F03%2F19%2F092656_45b7ad6b6c425ca6d7c951bc05e5d29e.png&h=8a2510e9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nbook左京成巴士真係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n個車站同JR站又遠<br />\n第一次搭又唔知佢唔係八重州個堆JR巴士<br />\n好彩預鬆左時間 如果較到炆一炆應該上唔到飛機了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"077a4da33b16ffb7120088cd2d5487d6830c7265","tid":597661,"uid":42344,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-19T03:10:20.000Z","msg":"livd"},{"pid":"91dd085d79ad2659e41bd642cf57a509cd5ef6ab","tid":597661,"uid":8203,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-19T03:53:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/19/114410_33c3da2127efa937964c4ee9a116d31c.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F03%2F19%2F114410_33c3da2127efa937964c4ee9a116d31c.png&h=7feb4a61&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/19/114414_39e3b7e18a52127dcb6bd45d2d6e08a8.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F03%2F19%2F114414_39e3b7e18a52127dcb6bd45d2d6e08a8.png&h=9509a7ec&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/19/114417_5f656bb6da779cd041796238b9dc2e9b.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F03%2F19%2F114417_5f656bb6da779cd041796238b9dc2e9b.png&h=e5b411ea&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/19/114422_26fa763cec9c5a4ffb95b16b521ad4d9.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F03%2F19%2F114422_26fa763cec9c5a4ffb95b16b521ad4d9.png&h=b03939f5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n第二次黎T3 個種「簡約樸素」既感覺都係一成不變<br />\n第一次搭香草<br />\n原來hand carrying一定幫你check到正一正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n而gate150就代表要搭巴士<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n上機了 空姐我比6.5/10"},{"pid":"5429ebff3c3cfe8d3414e05cebfe324f4cd3df0c","tid":597661,"uid":8203,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-19T04:00:34.000Z","msg":"講漏左一樣野<br />\n揀左心動香草佢會安排D閪位比你坐<br />\n明明我後面兩個空位安排左B位比我<br />\n仲要我呢到ABC坐滿<br />\n自問窮呀柒呀 不過搭UO想坐邊同地勤講都有得傾數<br />\n而而家我就逼到仆街<br />\n<br />\n我見到有D POST鬧UO話坐廉航都揀香草<br />\n我真係笑而不語<br />\n有得撚一定唔會再揀香草<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"64de744f021050e3ced3e262a822744a72ad9af2","tid":597661,"uid":60260,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d265fcb694c10d0307bfdb325a7f43ddf8c25ad1","tid":597661,"uid":8203,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-19T01:29:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/19/092656_45b7ad6b6c425ca6d7c951bc05e5d29e.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F03%2F19%2F092656_45b7ad6b6c425ca6d7c951bc05e5d29e.png&h=8a2510e9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nbook左京成巴士真係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n個車站同JR站又遠<br />\n第一次搭又唔知佢唔係八重州個堆JR巴士<br />\n好彩預鬆左時間 如果較到炆一炆應該上唔到飛機了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-19T06:46:25.000Z","msg":"同你調轉，上次諗住搭巴士去河口湖，一開頭就以為係你呢個站搭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ca7086f099dec4dd12c1189a5fcf592d9dc46f0f","tid":597661,"uid":8203,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-19T06:52:38.000Z","msg":"空姐講錯我比4/10<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/19/144954_e68dbf506ce828a3c6f0963cfe78016b.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F03%2F19%2F144954_e68dbf506ce828a3c6f0963cfe78016b.png&h=8fd96120&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/19/144956_fc217e14d28051584aac994c0edc2e08.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F03%2F19%2F144956_fc217e14d28051584aac994c0edc2e08.png&h=5b742fa3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n今日六點半起身到而家終於到函館<br />\n一直係交通工具上（大概5個鐘） <br />\n落機係成肚胃氣定唔知咩氣 勁唔舒服<br />\n岩岩到左airbnb homestay<br />\n痾屁，沖涼，瞓覺<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n夜晚有咩好食勞煩推薦下<br />\n利申唔食生冷野<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d976ec664012268b3ec2fda97c22e6eb84298dfd","tid":597661,"uid":50553,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-19T06:56:16.000Z","msg":"今晚是但隊啲野落肚朝早去朝市食啦<br />\nBtw住邊頭?"},{"pid":"30a31b959767ea84348e8fb0baa2a004c71e3bfe","tid":597661,"uid":42344,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-19T07:12:14.000Z","msg":"唔上函館山？"},{"pid":"b73f65ce1e03431957c70014a7ead3635d6e0976","tid":597661,"uid":40433,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-19T07:59:50.000Z","msg":"小丑漢堡"},{"pid":"2a6dd0b431ec5576f322beb6aa96c0453810faf5","tid":597661,"uid":8203,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d976ec664012268b3ec2fda97c22e6eb84298dfd","tid":597661,"uid":50553,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-19T06:56:16.000Z","msg":"今晚是但隊啲野落肚朝早去朝市食啦<br />\nBtw住邊頭?"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-19T10:44:47.000Z","msg":"唔食生野去朝市都有野食咩<br />\n想釣章魚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n住JR站十分鐘路程"},{"pid":"9869246a774a42aca73c1c90618ad358359c7dc0","tid":597661,"uid":8203,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-19T10:47:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/19/184511_d4db3306d4870791ea7913467cb1d367.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F03%2F19%2F184511_d4db3306d4870791ea7913467cb1d367.png&h=2bda1e14&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/19/184513_93f30f3306c8a037ef9601761a7f72a6.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F03%2F19%2F184513_93f30f3306c8a037ef9601761a7f72a6.png&h=a38a3a0d&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/19/184515_6a3d1357f41546de9ae99f25e0ad383e.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F03%2F19%2F184515_6a3d1357f41546de9ae99f25e0ad383e.png&h=dd3d35c6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n岩岩host好好人帶左我地遊覽函館<br />\n分享下函館人先知既野<br />\n譬如有d坂會有融雪道路系統 有d無<br />\n要揀黎行<br />\n所以有d外地人/外國人唔知就會係結冰既坂瀡滑梯<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1ed8531a275b2fa9fd87db71699855d94e7a70a5","tid":597661,"uid":8203,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"30a31b959767ea84348e8fb0baa2a004c71e3bfe","tid":597661,"uid":42344,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-19T07:12:14.000Z","msg":"唔上函館山？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-19T12:35:35.000Z","msg":"第一日就去？"},{"pid":"000e8914be95aa56f171bcc00f8b4d9278fc934a","tid":597661,"uid":42344,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1ed8531a275b2fa9fd87db71699855d94e7a70a5","tid":597661,"uid":8203,"like":0,"dislike":0