g src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/21/104414_4f2a1f6a2c790434d906c972f9b8d601.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F03%2F21%2F104414_4f2a1f6a2c790434d906c972f9b8d601.png&h=08b6b3db&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/21/104418_57975bbdbb4800ab94426143f6b029f2.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F03%2F21%2F104418_57975bbdbb4800ab94426143f6b029f2.png&h=e6015626&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n道路上，函館既市容唔係咁好<br />\n無非都係因為要剷雪到路既一旁<br />\n而融左之後D砂石就會留低係度<br />\n聽host講 函館市人口偏老年人口<br />\n後生都去左新幹線站個頭<br />\n所以行街會覺得靜同埋無乜活力<br />\n喵星人會匿埋車尾既傳說好似第一次親眼目睹<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n所以大雪地區駕駛前會先拍下部車趕走佢地先<br />\n函館的確比想像中細 行7-10分鐘就到朝市了<br />\n今年聽聞蟹收穫唔多 較往年貴好多<br />\n普通size帝王蟹就四萬up 最大接近六萬一隻<br />\n窮就惟有食蟹饅 630一隻帝王饅<br />\n得罪講句個包做得唔好 蟹肉亦都唔夠香<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1960228ef1c88f4b5de36433732494551961d390","tid":597661,"uid":8203,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1addcfb6fa9379a3f276210a1f0a0aa9773c0472","tid":597661,"uid":100131,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"075159971ea36adab74d759ebfcc2aeba6d53ce5","tid":597661,"uid":8203,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-21T02:02:58.000Z","msg":"毒撚開po無人理<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-21T02:21:20.000Z","msg":"你唔知呢度開旅遊post 都係有人睇無人應嘅咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/36.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-21T03:17:58.000Z","msg":"你要知道你既回覆係我出po既動力<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/07.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/07.png\" class