https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/21/223111_0fd19155c1a51c54de079ef2f86dec43.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F03%2F21%2F223111_0fd19155c1a51c54de079ef2f86dec43.png&h=8144a3ab&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/21/223116_21e22539b2c27788793cbf4b941cac68.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F03%2F21%2F223116_21e22539b2c27788793cbf4b941cac68.png&h=3dd4dc26&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/21/223119_4c8c48cec7d3f8b166a68cbad14d0ca5.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F03%2F21%2F223119_4c8c48cec7d3f8b166a68cbad14d0ca5.png&h=0d2d7095&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n大家都知道食海鮮唔係一件便宜事<br />\n但估唔到竟然有間鋪頭賣500円一碗丼<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n真係算抵食 唔食得生野個set食羊肉丼加燒三文魚身<br />\n都幾好食 不過不失<br />\n食完落去格離個室內市場見到個阿伯<br />\n賣手工作 都係函館大路既手信野<br />\n最正係有得同佢吹水 <br />\n佢為人幽默 寫晒筆記紀錄低外國語<br />\n同客人有講有笑<br />\n仲可以扮下蟹影相<br />\n大家去到都搵下佢玩下啦<br />\n旅行最開心不過既事唔係同當地人互動咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n最後都好開心咁買左幾樣野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8b050a2c239da62d9d508beb31f35eb763d01988","tid":597661,"uid":42344,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-21T15:41:47.000Z","msg":"500YEN咁抵"},{"pid":"870d0902373015529c096e30cac8f30329a2e85b","tid":597661,"uid":5958,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-21T15:47:33.000Z","msg":"正呀函館<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4929a71e1c826eda047959deb0500356e4d21cc8","tid":597661,"uid":8203,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-22T08:27:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018